---

const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h4 class="footer-title">我的博客</h4>
      <p class="footer-desc">一款关于独立博客经营的模拟经营游戏</p>
      <p class="footer-tagline">一个互联网游民的博客成长之路</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h4 class="footer-title">链接</h4>
      <ul class="footer-links">
        <li><a href="/">首页</a></li>
        <li><a href="/download">下载游戏</a></li>
        <li><a href="/sponsor">赞助支持</a></li>
        <li><a href="/circle">博客圈子</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h4 class="footer-title">技术栈</h4>
      <ul class="footer-links">
        <li><span class="nes-text is-disabled">Godot 4.7</span></li>
        <li><span class="nes-text is-disabled">GDScript</span></li>
        <li><span class="nes-text is-disabled">Pixel Art</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-bottom">
    <p>&copy; {currentYear} bosichong. <a href="/LICENSE" class="license-link">MIT License</a>.</p>
    <p class="nes-text is-disabled" style="font-size:0.8rem;">Powered by Astro + NES.css</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    background: #0a0a0a;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--accent);
    margin-top: auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem 0;
  }

  .footer-inner {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .footer-title {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .footer-desc {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .footer-tagline {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .footer-links {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .footer-links li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .footer-links a {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .footer-links a:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 2rem auto 0;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .license-link {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .license-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .footer-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
